{"tid":1604309,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"適當性暴力執法？香港女示威者遭搶扯露胸罩 網民痛斥黑警","createTime":"2019-09-30T02:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T04:31:22.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0b05f4196546c12c475adcc5830bd092ab0fef58","tid":1604309,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2931013_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2931013_1_1.jpg&h=d17ec422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港「929全球反極權大遊行」，香港鎮暴警察不但在逮捕行動中使用殘忍手段，還強扯一名被捕女示威者的上衣，使她在光天化日下露出內衣，在香港網路討論區「連登」引發眾怒，網民紛紛痛批「禽獸」、「黑警仆街死全家」！<br />\n<br />\n這已不是港警第一次傳出性暴力執法。6月12日，有女示威者被多名男警拖行，過程上衣被掀起，露出內衣；8月4日「天水圍」行動則傳出有女示威者遭警方扯下裙子和內褲，下體全走光；8月10日「大埔上街」遊行中，有名白衣少女遭港警撲倒壓制，過程中遭警察扯上衣，摸大腿內側。<br />\n<br />\n8月31日「反送中#MeToo」集會中，有示威者就指控港警，在扣留一名女示威者時，以硬物摩擦她下體，還餵食她利尿劑不讓她上廁所，讓她當場尿失禁出醜。<br />\n<br />\n6月以來的多場反送中運動，已經造成香港警民之間的對立。網傳8月11日一名被捕女子遭到警員輪暴，港警則嚴正駁斥這項指控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2931013_2_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2931013_2_1.jpg&h=3a497f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8月4日「天水圍」行動則傳出有女示威者遭警方扯下裙子和內褲，下體全走光。（擷取自臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2931013_3_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2931013_3_1.jpg&h=d58b141f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8月10日「大埔上街」遊行中，一名少女只是路過當地，就遭港警撲倒壓制，過程中還扯其衣，摸其大腿內側，讓現場目睹此幕民眾怒不可遏。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2931013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2931013&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1dkum%2F%2B3HP0Ta45uqRfUpIg%3D&h=dc098cb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2931013&h=ad1309de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2931013</a>"},{"pid":"65e9510f1decbdd5d0209e6e8b36dc17c8ab85c4","tid":1604309,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cafd8b083a6e42b6486a4c7889488716cf3e17","tid":1604309,"uid":135127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d52cfa4094d4d7b09233a10b9843e9d1cc6dfa14","tid":1604309,"uid":43204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkohL5A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkohL5A.jpg&h=d68b75ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"710a699f371da3d843b97268138c120a5c324e7b","tid":1604309,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d06cbf8fdb188f949d11e6d50d280c56dfb5e08","tid":1604309,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:31:22.000Z","msg":"13:00<br />\n荃灣 - 沙咀道球場<br />\n黃大仙 - 黃大仙廣場<br />\n屯門 - 政府合署<br />\n灣仔 - 修頓球場<br />\n深水埗 - 楓樹街球場<br />\n沙田 - 車公廟"}]}